{
  "abstract": "Groundnut foliar fungal diseases, stem and pod rots, and wilt cause severe pod yield losses world wide , while aflatoxin \r\ncontamination causes serious quality problems. This information bulletin updates the list of sources of resistance to six\r\nimportant fungal and bacterial diseases and provides information on some of their agronomic traits and reaction to other\r\ndiseases. Merits and demerits of these resistance sources that may influence their usage in different situations \r\nare highlighted.",
